{"tid":1317610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一個懦弱阿叔，憤怒得只剩下錢。","createTime":"2019-07-14T19:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T20:25:01.000Z","uid":238809,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"73a7e0051ecb42175792a7197027be39cbea70d1","tid":1317610,"uid":238809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:43:18.000Z","msg":"我係一個近四十歲既阿叔。我不停俾藉口自己唔出街同你班細路衝。眼見你地十四五歲瘦弱既女同學都戴哂眼罩準備衝。真係好慚愧。淨係上網like下post不停屌政府差佬乜都冇做。對你地唔住！<br />\n我相信我和大多和理非既撚頭一樣會投票會屌，亦有大把多餘錢。現在只有這個方法支持大家。要眾籌募捐乜撚都好出聲便是了！<br />\n對唔住！！！"},{"pid":"7de01ea75a7300c84bed4cbf2fc2c42a0f956ca1","tid":1317610,"uid":41545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:44:57.000Z","msg":"足矣"},{"pid":"4a7f786ef6887c28ca0102826350ab7a1e01a55d","tid":1317610,"uid":208931,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:46:18.000Z","msg":"我地候生出錢出力<br />\n你地有家庭負擔唔出力 出錢出物資<br />\n你地都好緊要架！<br />\n大家一齊加油<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25160683f581d4ae1b5295e1793eb442e992206","tid":1317610,"uid":122001,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2kMTn5f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2kMTn5f.png&h=500659f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cfac1d69664bdd557ac2fbfe0e0559946b75ef1","tid":1317610,"uid":32063,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:48:51.000Z","msg":"其實我一直都話 D人話自己廢老唔得架啦係唔岩<br />\n當年我哋都唔會話自己廢你哋做咩撚野<br />\n你每人買多D較剪索帶噴漆<br />\n口罩白衫眼罩保鮮紙<br />\n再把炮call車運野<br />\n比d年輕人都好 （學術研究 不鼓勵暴力）<br />\n想做野一定要做到 <br />\n自己搵野做啦"},{"pid":"6397890eaecd56653cfa640e4f095e454d6d6d15","tid":1317610,"uid":76332,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T1